member.Description: Still loving the Triathlon sport, Now have competed for over 16 years and training for my third Ironman race in Melbourne 2014. Having a bit of trouble with my tendon around the left knee. But still well enough to do enough training without too much pain. Did not do well at the City to surf 2013, succumbing to too much pain and ended up walking the last 2 k's of a 14 k run!
